title: Widdershins Volumes 1-3 (2012->|Dgtl-HR|Son of Ultron-Empire)
description:
Overview:


    " For failed wizard Sidney Malik, it's been a rather trying day.

      Threatened with eviction, expelled from university, arrested, and accidentally
      crowned the King of Thieves, he'll need more than a few magic tricks to get
      himself out of this. Luckily for him, he's attracted the attention of chain-
      smoking bounty hunter Harriet Barber, who'll either save him or get him into
      even deeper trouble, perhaps both.

      [... S]et in 1830s Widdershins, an English town unlike any other. " 


     --  "Widdershins - Sleight of Hand", back cover




Contains:


   Widdershins - Volume I   - Sleight of Hand        (2012) (Digital-HR) (Empire)

   Widdershins - Volume II  - No Rest for the Wicked (2013) (Digital-HR) (Empire)

   Widdershins - Volume III - Vanishing Act          (2013) (Digital-HR) (Empire)
